<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/17980745-how-the-west-won"><img alt="How the West Won: The Neglected Story of the Triumph of Modernity" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1385522079l/17980745._SX98_.jpg" />
